OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784017089
OL,3,C2,700 deaths linked to May and June
OL,4,Cheatwaves as climate change impacts UK
OL,6,FShe warned that while heatwaves
OL,7,Fprompted news images of people eating
OL,8,Fice cream and sunbathing on beaches,
OL,9,F"people need to be aware that we are
OL,10,Fnow seeing dangerous climate-change
OL,11,Ffuelled heat that is claiming lives,
OL,12,Fdisrupting schools and hospitals and
OL,13,Fshutting down transport and
OL,14,Finfrastructure".
OL,26,@qD@AOUvD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
