OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784017089
OL,3,C2,700 deaths linked to May and June
OL,4,Cheatwaves as climate change impacts UK
OL,6,FThe independent advisory Climate
OL,7,FChange Committee has warned that the
OL,8,FUK is unprepared for extreme heat,
OL,9,Fwhich could see 92% of homes
OL,10,Foverheating by mid-century, and has
OL,11,Fcalled for maximum temperature rules
OL,12,Fin workplaces and air conditioning in
OL,13,Fhospitals, care homes and schools.
OL,15,FThe team behind the estimates said
OL,16,Ftheir models had produced mortality
OL,17,Festimates comparable to those issued
OL,18,Fby the UKHSA for past heat events.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
