OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784017089
OL,3,C2,700 deaths linked to May and June
OL,4,Cheatwaves as climate change impacts UK
OL,6,FThe UKHSA is due to publish its
OL,7,Fofficial interim analysis of heat-
OL,8,Fdeath impacts of the recent heatwaves,
OL,9,Fbased on mortality data in the coming
OL,10,Fweeks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
